    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK916">
<l>tannalam pārippār tōyār takaicerukkip</l>
<l>puṉṉalam pārippār tōḷ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who would spread (the fame of) their own goodness will not desire the shoulders of those,who rejoice in their accomplishments and bestow their despicable favours (on all who pay).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
